exitCode: 1
stdout:

stderr:
Error: agent-browser is not installed.

dor ab drives your own agent-browser binary, which Dormouse never bundles.
Install it, then re-run your command:

    npm i -g agent-browser

More: https://agent-browser.dev
Already installed? Make sure it's on your PATH, or set DORMOUSE_AGENT_BROWSER_BIN to its full path.
